Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all soggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wonder Hill! \N Let's Have Lots of Fun! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Runny Porridge\NWelcome to Wonder Hill! \N Let's Have Lots of Fun! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wonder Hill! \N Let's Have Lots of Fun! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally get a vacation, and now this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no different from work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can fix the clock, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna finish up and mingle, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...why did the cog suddenly get out of whack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Brush not helping out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot see the light of Eos. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Eos"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I... lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won, but... wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he seemed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! Now I can finally have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji! Yu-yu is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Danji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the picture of health!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu! Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me! Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu is... Yu-yu is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, he seems to have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a fever?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His throat isn't swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,His throat isn't swollen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji! Quiet down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel a little crummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep will take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, take him to the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cold, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu! I'll teach you how a man cures a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First: to bring down your fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: to give you nourishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then: to wrap a leek around your neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?! All better now, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotten worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, looks like I'd better take him in \Nand nurse him back to health at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your house is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A man needs quiet to fight off a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're clearly the more dangerous one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll care for him with full attention to detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll report you for unlawful confinement!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him to me!\NUh, no, I will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Me!\NNo, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, m--\NNo, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him to the doctor first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hospital 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Examination Room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A fever brought on by abrupt stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Abrupt stress, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The hospital beds are full,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's mild enough for him \Nto recover fine at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got work, right, Tomari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll drive Yu-yu home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to tell Akiko and the rest about what--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What souvenir would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko, are you three on a trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What the? Danji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're at a hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We invited Yu-yu, but he said, "No thanks, \NI'll be spending time with Danji and the gang."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be what they call growing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes a big sister feel lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Yu-yu's running a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Yu-yu has a fever?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't go home now, surely?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear! Whatever shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll manage something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take him to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, are you fine with this \Nleading to a criminal case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't poke fun at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told them \NI'll manage something for this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Apples, leeks -> for sore throat \N - Jelly sports drink if no appetite \N - Don't let him get worked up, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That Tomari...\N- Apples, leeks -> for sore throat \N - Jelly sports drink if no appetite \N - Don't let him get worked up, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I already knew what he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yogurt / Whole Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooling Strips (contains 5)\NYogurt / Whole Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Would he need these?\NCooling Strips (contains 5)\NYogurt / Whole Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Classical Music for a Good Night's Sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this, too?\NClassical Music for a Good Night's Sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since \NI've taken care of a sick person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaku-E 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I oughta catch a cold, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for holding down the fort, Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just guessed he'd sleep better \Nwith this guy next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's not a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there's nobody at your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'll stay here until tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to cause you all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. You're still feverish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I think it's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand's hot, so I can't really tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji Momoyama's Japanese man food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... homemade?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I even pickled the plum myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great for a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so tasty that you're crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What the? Doesn't suit your taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says they're sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this, then sleep some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sleepy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A sick person's gotta sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with such a slight build, \Nyou bared your fangs at Tohya,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and overexerted yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is the place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unmistakably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let us in, it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why did you all show up?\NJust let us in, it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, this feels like a man's castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, no place to sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I toss these aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it! What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To pay our dear Yu-yu a get-well visit, why else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you're already up and better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My fever's gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I set out cushions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be treating this place \Nlike it's your own home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... sorry to barge in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Bro's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here to see Yu-yu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave your get-well gifts and scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Danji, they took the trouble to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As kind-hearted as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my get-well gift for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A li'l doctor's kit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Breaking a sweat is great for your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, he caught a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to wear this next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that your hobby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! I already have that playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Yu-yu's happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll let it go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get well soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's time for bed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! I really am all bet--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This will decide if you're better or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See? All better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You got quite a lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You could put together a full deck with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's strong... and this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This one, too! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He was tough, huh? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But you won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried so hard, you got a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you won, there shouldn't be \Nanything lingering from the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Something does linger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...is hurting because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that guy. He's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I still don't... \Nlike seeing anyone suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're all better, \Nwanna join me in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The water's boiling now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji, what kind of music do you listen to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mature music, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jazz!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That was harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a punishment for lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bath will be ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use the bath first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine going later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That was revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fold laundry in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'll help out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days' worth is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,About a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I totally forgot to think on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...really love Vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One more fight! Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! Bath time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji! Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You worry too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna worry while I still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This next one, then bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That great look in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wonder Hill! \N Let's Have Lots of Fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Danji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I ache all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Danji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I used your kitchen without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You fried up these eggs, Yu-yu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have one, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got yolk on your lip.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy moley, that gave my stomach a thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.55,0:22:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I leave the door unlocked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of a thief's tricks: lock-picking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Secure your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A cop shouldn't commit crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Yu-yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all better!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji seems to have nursed you back to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was a piece of cake! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:22:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go out to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, I know a great local place!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just Hachiban Ramen! 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.39,0:23:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've got your appetite back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to you, Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Them's fighting words.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't order all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I ordered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up, it's to celebrate your recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here's a present from me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And some free bamboo shoots from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.14,0:23:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! I'll have another bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll have another, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Then, I'll have large seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And thirds! Keep 'em coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.53,0:23:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Zakky?\NAnd thirds! Keep 'em coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd better keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have extra-large seconds.\NOh, I'd better keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Extra-large?!\NOh, I'd better keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.41,0:25:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.98,0:25:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.93,0:26:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm introducing my deck's \Nace in the hole: "Diabolos Boys, Eden"!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.34,0:26:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To indicate just how amazing this one is:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.01,0:26:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Mt. Fuji in a New Year's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.31,0:26:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a strawberry on shortcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.86,0:26:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a piece of octopus \Nin a batch of fried anchovies!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.46,0:26:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! That's not enough explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.19,0:26:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.53,0:26:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, it's a cool and tough unit \Nthat hits the enemy line like a hurricane! 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.45,0:26:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.20,0:26:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.21,0:26:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a Fish and Water 
